 Performance indicators (sensitivity, specificity, positive predictive value, PPV, negative predictive value, NPV and their 95%CI) of individual markers and whole GastroPanel test will be calculated separately for each study endpoint, using the STATA/SE software and the diagti algorithm introduced by Seed et al.

